==English==

===Pronunciation===

*{{AHD|ə-dăpʹtər}}

{{wikipedia}}
===Noun===
'''adapter''' or '''adaptor'''
# One that adapts, such as a device used to achieve operative compatibility between devices that otherwise are incompatible.
# (''British'' etc) A [[device]] that permits two or three [[plug]]s to be used on one [[electrical]] [[power]] [[point]]; a device that allows one [[format]] of plug to be used with a different format of [[socket]].

